'''mermaid 
sequenceDiagram
participant Attacker
participant BotNet
participant WebServer
participant Firewall
'''
    Attacker->>+BotNet: attack bots
    BotNet->>+Attacker: bots infected
    Attacker->>+BotNet: attack servers
    BotNet->>+WebServer: attack initiated 
    WebServer->>+Firewall: web server affected analyze traffic 
    Firewall->>+WebServer: analyzing data
    Firewall->>+WebServer: irregualrity detected 
    WebServer->>+BotNet: firewall initiated
    Firewall->>+BotNet: repell attack 
    BotNet->>+Attacker: attack repelled 

attacker attempts to hack servers and infects bots. infected bots target servers. firewall detect irregularities and deploys. preventing the attack.  
